    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/7f26dc61bb6e1dae1ac8f55ac77283eb.avif?t=1750707050\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻松愉快的全新体验，也可挑战你的策略极限，《超增税都市》——化身税收狂魔吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合城市建设与 Roguelite，你需要从随机设施中精妙组合、动态布局，打造赚钱机器；烧脑决策、硬核挑战，快来开启城建幻想，征服环环相扣的盈利迷宫！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于演示版</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是《超级增税城市》的演示版。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以体验一些设施、物品和阶段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仅演示版就非常有趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >规则</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从3个选项里选择设施，布置在地图上吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/d02885f65436c160a365fd2999d0a3ce.poster.avif?t=1750707050\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/d02885f65436c160a365fd2999d0a3ce.webm?t=1750707050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/d02885f65436c160a365fd2999d0a3ce.mp4?t=1750707050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机移动的住民只要进入设施工作后就能拿到报酬！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/b951bcac73b4744e8a660ff5faad17de.poster.avif?t=1750707050\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/b951bcac73b4744e8a660ff5faad17de.webm?t=1750707050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/b951bcac73b4744e8a660ff5faad17de.mp4?t=1750707050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >限定时间结束后就是交税的时间啦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用赚来的钱交税吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/2c12ff7f56641005f5812cf66c40c6b4.poster.avif?t=1750707050\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/2c12ff7f56641005f5812cf66c40c6b4.webm?t=1750707050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/2c12ff7f56641005f5812cf66c40c6b4.mp4?t=1750707050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于设施</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用50种以上的道具来强化你的街道吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/625a3b5c3ca86292ff4fb0d0e7247fcc.poster.avif?t=1750707050\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/625a3b5c3ca86292ff4fb0d0e7247fcc.webm?t=1750707050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/625a3b5c3ca86292ff4fb0d0e7247fcc.mp4?t=1750707050\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于道具</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用20种以上的道具来强化你的街道吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133750/extras/16d3d1cccbfc2817942b3fd637cd2d93.poster.avif?t=1750